{"tid":1285464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想輕生嘅同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T04:15:50.000Z","uid":104917,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea2752357551f4a53ef62a66a67fa1829df2b057","tid":1285464,"uid":104917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"我見到已經有好多專家、巴絲們講過<br />\n繼續「死諫」只會<span style=\"color: orange;\">淡化之前戰友嘅犧牲</span><br />\n繼續「死諫」只會令犧牲咗嘅戰友變成單純而又毫無感情嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\">數字</span><br />\n<br />\n我唔知你地究竟對現況或者將來有幾灰心<br />\n灰心到你地甘心就咁離開我地成班手足<br />\n其實你地都好明白<span style=\"color: orange;\">巴絲們都好關心你地</span><br />\n呢幾日一有企跳嘅事件發生<br />\n巴絲們都好緊張好擔心<br />\n甚麼<span style=\"color: orange;\">拋開私事出去搵人搵足全日</span><br />\n<br />\n我講咁多其實係想拜託你地一件事：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">考慮下我地呢班關心你地嘅巴絲</span></span><br />\n即使我地幾堅強都好<br />\n都受唔住眼白白睇住自己嘅手足一個又一個離開<br />\n嗰種心力交瘁<br />\n嗰種無力感<br />\n嗰種痛恨自己救唔到自己重要嘅手足嘅感覺<br />\n其實比因為香港而灰心嘅灰心<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更加灰心、更加痛</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以求下你地<br />\n顧念下我地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好放開我地嘅手<br />\n唔好推開我地<br />\n唔好拋棄我地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好唔好？"},{"pid":"4028b5c41548d9ab568bd8dd9427e0a009b459b5","tid":1285464,"uid":53840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:38:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d55089a909a78314af990715b48e86bab01a6b3","tid":1285464,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:39:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4fda29496e1c53ef020244ac0efa3559740f076","tid":1285464,"uid":104917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"希望多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2710aa5d37fbd0f239bbd6442408eb445b3e3d","tid":1285464,"uid":104917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"附上一堆貓主子<br />\n<br />\n情緒好差想睇貓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285982</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}